        <mxCell id="amplio" parent="solon" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#2E7D32;strokeColor=#1B5E20;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Amplio Process Engine&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Solon reference processes — UNMODIFIED&#xa;(used as design reference only)&#xa;&#xa;DWP BPMN deployed alongside:&#xa;• dcms-intake-and-first-contact.bpmn  Flow 1  Low&#xa;• dcms-vulnerability-to-resolution.bpmn  Flow 2  Med&#xa;• dcms-payment-monitoring.bpmn  Flows 2+3  Low&#xa;• dcms-breach-to-placement.bpmn  Flow 3  ⚠ HIGH&#xa;• dcms-strategy-review.bpmn  Flow 5  Low&#xa;&#xa;Flows 4 &amp; 6: no new BPMN required" vertex="1">
