        <mxCell id="amplio-constraints" parent="solon" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E65100;strokeColor=#BF360C;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Amplio Authoring Constraints — all DCMS BPMN&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• Parallel Gateway: sequential-only (branches do not execute concurrently)&#xa;• Script Tasks: FEEL expressions only — no Groovy or JavaScript&#xa;• Business Rule Tasks → Service Task → Drools KIE POST /drools-runtime/execute-stateless/{containerId}&#xa;• Compensation events not implemented → use explicit error boundary + compensation logic&#xa;• Kafka: only topics confirmed in integration guide §5" vertex="1">
