        <mxCell id="db" parent="solon" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#2E7D32;strokeColor=#1B5E20;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;" value="PostgreSQL 16  —  Solon schema + DCMS additions  |  Liquibase (Solon-managed)  |  DWP fields as Data Area JSONB on Taxpayer / Case / Suppression / Task  |  New tables: dcms_strategy_version · champion_challenger_assignment" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="1580" x="10" y="488" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="e-custom-db" edge="1" parent="solon" source="custom-band" style="endArrow=block;endFill=1;html=1;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.25;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#AAAAAA;" target="db">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="e-gw-solon" edge="1" parent="1" source="gw" style="endArrow=open;endFill=0;html=1;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;exitX=0.15;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.15;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#888888;" target="amplio">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="blockers" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#B71C1C;strokeColor=#7F0000;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;⛔ OPEN BLOCKERS — gate integration design lock&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Blocker 1 — Kafka command-name discrepancy&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;Platform-reference 24-command names (PostPaymentCommand, WriteOffDebtCommand…)&#xa;not confirmed as externally-publishable Kafka topics.&#xa;irm.bpmn-engine.* topics are engine-internal.&#xa;Resolution: inspect Kafka producer config + revenue-management-be-custom&#xa;from Solon codebase. If commands are not externally publishable, redesign&#xa;inter-layer contract around the actual publishable surface.&#xa;Verify: topic names · payload schemas · response events · consumer-group isolation.&#xa;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Blocker 3 — MHCM SuppressionExpiryJob behaviour&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;Behaviour of SuppressionExpiryJob when maximumNumberDays=0 is undocumented.&#xa;If job treats 0 as &#39;already expired&#39;, MHCM suppressions are silently lifted without&#xa;professional sign-off = breach of Reg 21 Debt Respite Scheme Regs 2020.&#xa;Resolution: read SuppressionExpiryJob source from Solon codebase.&#xa;If &#39;already expired&#39;: never set maxDays=0; use maxDays=36500 +&#xa;overrideEndDateSW=true + DCMS-owned ReleaseSuppressionCommand release path.&#xa;Document as known operational risk.&#xa;&#xa;Blocker 2 (REST API stability for sync queries) not applicable to Option A." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="540" x="10" y="760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="risks" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E65100;strokeColor=#BF360C;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Option A — Key Risks&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;HIGH  Flow 3 (dcms-breach-to-placement.bpmn) authoring complexity&#xa;        PTP loop · supervisor branching · inter-process message correlation&#xa;        Design + Amplio-constraint-validate before build sprint. Timebox 2 days.&#xa;&#xa;HIGH  Blocker 1 blocks intake trigger — if no external Kafka topic,&#xa;        intake process cannot start via Kafka. Fallback: REST polling.&#xa;&#xa;HIGH  Drools DRL developer-gated for new rule types.&#xa;        Accept for Release 1; parameterised template library workaround;&#xa;        DWP sign-off required.&#xa;&#xa;HIGH  Java 17 / Liquibase hard constraint — no escape path within Option A.&#xa;&#xa;MED   Operations dashboard: no analytics DB buffer — REST queries at query time.&#xa;        Early performance spike required. Add read-model tables incrementally.&#xa;&#xa;MED   C/C + IE engine structurally awkward in Solon extension module.&#xa;        Define internal hexagonal boundaries from day one." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="530" x="562" y="750" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ui-constraints" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#0D47A1;strokeColor=#0A2F6B;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;UI Hard Constraints under Option A&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;CANNOT DO&#xa;✗  Live C/C results from real operational data pipeline&#xa;     (no analytics pipeline — pre-computed historical data only)&#xa;✗  Fully interactive historical simulation&#xa;     (no sandbox engine — pre-computed snapshot only)&#xa;✗  Non-technical new rule type authoring&#xa;     (Drools DRL requires a developer — template library only)&#xa;✗  Strategy diff across arbitrary non-consecutive versions&#xa;✗  UI shape decoupled from Solon API structure&#xa;     (thin BFF — gaps discovered iteratively per screen)&#xa;✗  Dashboard drill-down backed by analytics database&#xa;     (all data from Solon REST + DCMS JSONB at query time)&#xa;&#xa;CAN DO&#xa;✓  All three workspaces present and role-gated&#xa;✓  Case Worker: full case screen, I&amp;E, restriction flags, arrangement&#xa;✓  Operations: queue health, SLA, bulk reassignment, vuln exceptions&#xa;✓  Configuration: strategy versioning, peer review, RBAC, reference data" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="522" x="1112" y="750" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="footer" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=9;fontColor=#616161;" value="&lt;i&gt;Option A: DCMS extends Solon in-process. Five new BPMN definitions authored from scratch. Solon reference processes unmodified. Two new DB tables. Blockers 1 and 3 must be resolved via Solon codebase inspection before integration design lock.&lt;/i&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="1614" x="20" y="980" as="geometry" />
